picard.sam.markduplicates.util

Interface OpticalDuplicateFinder.PhysicalLocation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PhysicalLocationForMateCigar, ReadEnds, ReadEndsForMarkDuplicates, ReadEndsForMarkDuplicatesWithBarcodes, ReadEndsForMateCigar
    Enclosing class:
    OpticalDuplicateFinder

    public static interface OpticalDuplicateFinder.PhysicalLocation
    Small interface that provides access to the physical location information about a cluster. All values should be defaulted to -1 if unavailable. ReadGroup and Tile should only allow non-zero positive integers, x and y coordinates may be negative.
